thub.com/users/RobBotic1/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobBotic1/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobBotic1/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobBotic1/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobBotic1/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-09-15T14:04:53Z","updated_at":"2022-09-15T14:04:53Z","body":"Thanks! I'm thrilled that I could help!\r\n\r\nAs I see (for HTTP) CURLOPT_HTTPGET, CURLOPT_NOBODY, CURLOPT_UPLOAD, and CURLOPT_POST as mutually exclusive (I'm not certain about CURLOPT_CUSTOMREQUEST), I do have a question and two suggestions:\r\n- Should CURLOPT_NOBODY also be updated to set upload to false?\r\nhttps://github.com/curl/curl/blob/b98d45be27f71aa946f67138095c5479448fef95/lib/setopt.c#L342-L354\r\n- I would suggest updating the man page for CURLOPT_HTTPGET highlighting that it overrides CURLOPT_POST\r\nhttps://github.com/curl/curl/blob/b98d45be27f71aa946f67138095c5479448fef95/docs/libcurl/opts/CURLOPT_HTTPGET.3#L39-L40\r\n- I would suggest updating the man page for CURLOPT_POST (highlighting that it sets CURLOPT_UPLOAD to 0 and noting this issue for previous versions where CURLOPT_UPLOAD must be explicitly set to 0).\r\nhttps://github.com/curl/curl/blob/b98d45be27f71aa946f67138095c5479448fef95/docs/libcurl/opts/CURLOPT_POST.3#L65-L66","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/issues/comments/1248149287/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"RobBotic1","id":58122366,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU4MTIyMzY2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/58122366?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobBotic1","html_url":"https://github.com/RobBotic1","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/RobBotic1/foll